[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0483","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0768","title":"红帽 (Red Hat) 和 SUSE Linux Vixie Cron 服务 MAILTO 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 MAILTO 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 及 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.0/6.1 等系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制 cron 任务的 MAILTO 变量长度。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0768"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.067","remediation":"立即升级 vixie-cron 至 3.0.1-56 及以上版本（Red Hat）或安装 SUSE 对应安全补丁；若无法升级，在 crontab 中避免使用 MAILTO 变量或限制 MAILTO 值长度不超过 256 字节；建议迁移至现代 Linux 发行版（如 RHEL 8+），其 cronie 已内置该漏洞修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/602","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19470"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0482","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0767","title":"IBM AIX / Sun Solaris LC_MESSAGES 环境变量 libc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris libc 库、ufsrestore 及 rcp 工具在处理 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及 Sun Solaris 7.0 等 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复该问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0767"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.953","remediation":"对 Sun Solaris 7.0 系统，安装 Sun 安全补丁 107733-01 或更新版本；对 IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统，升级到 APAR IX89537 修复版本或安装对应 bos.rte.libc 补丁包。无法立即升级时，可通过在 /etc/environment 或 shell 启动脚本中过滤 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量（如 unset LC_MESSAGES）来缓解该缓冲区溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420557&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19217"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0481","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0764","title":"NetBSD NetBSD ARP 静态条目覆盖漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统 ARP 协议实现存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标网络发送伪造的 ARP 数据包，覆盖系统本应受保护的静态 ARP 缓存条目。攻击者利用此漏洞可实施中间人攻击或拒绝服务攻击，劫持或阻断目标主机与网络中其他设备的正常通信。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 系统，CVSS 评分 6.4。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0764"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.597","remediation":"立即升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本（1999 年 5 月已发布修复补丁），该版本内核已禁止 ARP 包覆盖静态 ARP 条目。如无法升级，可通过 `arp -s` 配合 `-f` 参数将静态 ARP 条目写入 `/etc/ethers` 并设置只读权限，同时在交换机上配置端口安全 (port security) 和动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 以限制 ARP 欺骗攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6539"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0480","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0480.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0763","title":"NetBSD 多宿主主机ARP表项跨网络修改漏洞","description":"NetBSD 在多宿主主机（配置多个网络接口连接不同子网）上存在 ARP 逻辑缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标主机的一个网络接口发送特制 ARP 数据包，该数据包会非法修改另一网络接口上的 ARP 缓存条目，导致跨网络 ARP 欺骗和中间人攻击。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞劫持不同网段间的流量，影响网络隔离性和数据机密性。受影响的系统包括运行 NetBSD 的多宿主主机配置。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0763"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.467","remediation":"建议升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.2 及以上版本，该版本修复了多宿主主机 ARP 跨接口污染问题。如无法升级，可在各网络接口分别设置静态 ARP 表项 (`arp -s`) 绑定关键网关和主机的 MAC 地址，同时启用内核参数 `net.inet.arp.allow_multicast=0` 过滤非法 ARP 响应，并在边界防火墙上限制非授权 ARP 数据包进入子网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6540"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0480.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0479","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0479.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0288","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 WINS 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 服务器在处理 UDP 137 端口（NetBIOS 名称服务）的数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送大量特制的无效 UDP 帧，导致 WINS 服务进程异常终止，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 之前的所有版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，利用方式简单，发送随机数据包洪流即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0288"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.717","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 WINS 服务对畸形 UDP 数据包的处理逻辑。如无法升级，在防火墙或主机层面阻止外部对 UDP 端口 137 (NETBIOS 名称服务) 的访问，仅允许可信内部网络通信。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://safenetworks.com/Windows/wins.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1233","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19238","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0288","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0288.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j989-83h4-x7f9/GHSA-j989-83h4-x7f9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wins_udp_flood.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0479.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0478","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0478.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0762","title":"Netscape Communicator 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 浏览器中存在信息泄露漏洞。当攻击者将恶意 JavaScript 代码嵌入 HTML 页面的 TITLE 标签中时，远程攻击者可利用浏览器的 \"about\" 协议获取用户的浏览器配置、浏览历史等敏感信息。攻击者需诱使用户访问恶意网页触发此漏洞。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0762"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.337","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 及以上版本，该版本修复了 TITLE 标签中 JavaScript 的权限控制缺陷。如无法升级，在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 可临时缓解攻击。由于 Netscape Communicator 已于 2008 年停止支持，建议迁移至 Firefox 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。若必须使用该旧版浏览器，可配置防火墙或代理规则拦截外部恶意脚本注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0762"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0478.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0477","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0761","title":"FreeBSD fts 库本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 fts 库例程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 periodic 程序触发该漏洞，导致任意文件被篡改。该漏洞源于 fts 库对文件路径名处理时未正确进行边界检查，攻击者利用精心构造的路径名可造成缓冲区溢出，进而修改系统关键文件，影响系统完整性与可用性。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0761"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.190","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 系统至 3.3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 fts 库例程中的缓冲区溢出问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，可安装 FreeBSD 安全公告提供的对应补丁包。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户对 periodic 程序的执行权限，移除不可信用户的 shell 访问，降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1074","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/644"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0476","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0476.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0286","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Web 服务器源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Web 服务器存在源代码泄露漏洞。远程攻击者通过在 URL 末尾添加一个空格字符，可绕过服务器对动态页面（如 ASP）的访问限制，从而读取活动页面的源代码。该漏洞允许攻击者获取数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息，为后续攻击提供信息基础，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0286"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.477","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，该更新已修复 IIS 对 URL 末尾空格的解析问题。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用不必要的脚本映射（如 .htr），或使用 URLScan 工具过滤包含空格的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0286","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0286","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0286.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mcjx-hw8r-r6gf/GHSA-mcjx-hw8r-r6gf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--66533299-dc62-42f2-95a8-8fa5e27069d0.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0476.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0475","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0475.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0285","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit 中包含的 telnet 工具存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标系统的 telnet 服务发起连接后立即关闭该连接，即可导致 telnet 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，造成目标系统无法正常提供 telnet 服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，无需任何前置权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0285"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.357","remediation":"立即卸载 Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit 中的 telnet.exe 工具，或将其重命名/移出系统路径以阻止调用。对于仍须使用 telnet 服务的环境，在防火墙层面限制仅信任 IP 可访问 23 端口，并升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0285","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0285.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0285","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82091/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0475.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0474","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0758","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 及 FastTrack 3.01 服务器存在源代码泄露漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者通过在脚本 URL 后附加 %20（URL 编码的空格字符），可导致服务器返回脚本源代码而非执行脚本，从而获取数据库连接凭证、业务逻辑等敏感信息。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需认证即可远程触发，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0758"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.743","remediation":"升级至 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 或更高版本，该版本已修复对 URL 中 %20 编码处理不当的问题。临时缓解措施：在反向代理或防火墙层配置规则，拦截以 \"%20\" 结尾的 .pl/.cgi 等脚本文件请求。鉴于该产品已停止维护多年，强烈建议迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等仍在积极维护的 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0758"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0473","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0284","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 4.0/5.0 及 Alt-N MDaemon 等 NT 邮件服务器的 SMTP 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送超长参数的 HELO 命令，可触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，仅需构造特制 SMTP 数据包即可实施攻击，影响范围广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0284"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.237","remediation":"升级 Microsoft Exchange Server 至 5.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题。对于 Alt-N MDaemon，升级至 2.72 或更高版本。如无法升级，在防火墙层面限制对 SMTP 端口（25/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许可信邮件服务器连接，并部署入侵检测规则拦截超长 HELO 参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0284","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23113","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0284","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0284.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mdaemon.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x9000/8622/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0282","title":"（已废弃）CVE-1999-0282 错误合并 SunOS loadmodule 两个独立漏洞的无效编号","description":"CVE-1999-0282 是一个已被官方驳回（REJECTED）的 CVE 编号，原因是它错误地将 CVE-1999-1584 和 CVE-1999-1586 两个不同漏洞的参考信息和描述合并为一条记录。NVD 已移除该编号下所有描述与引用，禁止继续使用。该编号不指向任何真实存在的漏洞，不存在可利用的攻击面或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:56.640","remediation":"CVE-1999-0282 已被撤销，请勿使用此编号。实际漏洞分别对应 CVE-1999-1584（SunOS 4.1.1–4.1.3c 及 Open Windows 3.0 中 loadmodule/modload 的本地权限提升）和 CVE-1999-1586（SunOS 4.1.x 中 xnews 调用的 loadmodule 未正确清理环境变量导致本地提权）。Sun 当时发布了补丁（如 Sun patch 100124-01），CERT 也发布了公告 CA-1993-18，但这些补丁现已无法获取。由于 SunOS 4.x 早已停止支持，建议将仍在运行的 SunOS 4.1.x 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Solaris 11、Linux 或 \\*BSD），同时严格控制 setuid/setgid 二进制文件的权限以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0468","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0281","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 URL长路径拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长 URL 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成服务不可用。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击门槛低，影响运行 IIS 2.0/3.0 的 Windows NT 系统。由于年代久远，微软已停止支持相关版本，建议升级至更高版本 IIS。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0281"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.960","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft IIS 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中启用 URL 长度限制（设置 MaxClientRequestBuffer 注册表值为 4096 字节），并在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务 80/443 端口的异常长 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0281","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20802","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0281","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0281.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5a605876-602f-4a7d-96cb-b788c024c2a8.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0281.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0466","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0280","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"微软 Internet Explorer 浏览器存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过构造特制的 .lnk 快捷方式文件或 .url 链接文件，诱使用户点击后在当前用户上下文环境中执行任意命令。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需身份认证，影响使用 Internet Explorer 的 Windows 系统。由于 IE 对 .lnk 和 .url 文件的处理缺乏充分校验，导致攻击者可在用户浏览网页时触发恶意操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0280"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.833","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，或安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-013 对应补丁。该漏洞已在新版 IE 中修复，建议立即停止使用旧版 IE，改用 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。如因兼容性必须使用，可在安全设置中将「Internet 区域」和「受限站点区域」的安全级别设为「高」，并禁用「下载未签名的 ActiveX 控件」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0280.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/CrackerCat/simpread/blob/1ec36a5827997f39a7a815e20121b12f8d781497/md/Chrome%20Browser%20Exploitation,%20Part%201:%20Introduction%20to%20V8%20and%20JavaScript%20Internals%20-%20Jack%20Hacks.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0465","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0465.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0279","title":"Excite Excite for Web Servers 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Excite for Web Servers（EWS）存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务提交包含 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号）的恶意请求，在服务进程中执行任意操作系统命令。该漏洞源于 EWS 对用户输入过滤不严，未正确处理 shell 特殊字符，导致攻击者可远程控制目标服务器。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0279"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.717","remediation":"Excite for Web Servers (EWS) 已停止维护多年，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至现代 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）替代 EWS。如无法立即迁移，在反向代理层过滤用户输入中的 shell 元字符（; | ` $ &）、严格限制 CGI 参数、并对 Web 服务目录实施最小权限访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0279","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0279","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisori